text: Galina Stepanova (born 26 February 1958) is a Soviet rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
